WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
We ask an AI assistant to send telemetry.

00:03.000 --> 00:05.700
It finds a risky endpoint.

00:05.700 --> 00:08.400
The safety gate checks the allow-list first.

00:08.400 --> 00:11.100
The unsafe call is blocked and recorded.

00:11.100 --> 00:13.700
The assistant switches to the approved service.

00:13.700 --> 00:16.000
That action is allowed, and the audit log keeps the record.
